---
title: Chicken Sausage & Spinach Ravioli Dinner’s Just 15 Minutes Away!
description: *Mamma mia!* Here’s some perfect pasta prepared at pronto speed. It starts with chopped tomato and pieces of chicken sausage that cook up quickly in a pan. Once you’ve got your water boiling, in go the ravioli, which become perfectly al dente in a flash since they’re fresh. After that, all you gotta do is stir in the creamy sauce and put it on a plate. Then you *mangiare!* *Mangiare!*! Just like mamma would’ve said.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e6b4e370d966827314656e6-2fe03fc2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/spinach-ricotta-ravioli-5e6b4e370d966827314656e6-d8f62120.pdf
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spinach-ricotta-ravioli-5e6b4e370d966827314656e6
time required: 15 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
